Troubleshooting Tips
Common Issues and Solutions
Sliver server won't start:

Check if port 8080 is already in use: sudo netstat -tulpn | grep :8080
Kill any existing processes: sudo pkill -f sliver
Restart with a different port: http --lport 8081
Implant not connecting:

Verify the HTTP listener is running: jobs in Sliver console
Check firewall settings: sudo ufw status
Ensure implant has execute permissions: chmod +x /tmp/PROPER_SNAKE
Persistence not working:

Check systemd service status: sudo systemctl status sliver-agent.service
Verify cron service is running: sudo systemctl status cron
Check file permissions on scripts
Permission denied errors:

Ensure scripts are executable: chmod +x script_name.sh
Run with appropriate privileges: sudo for system-level operations
Check file ownership: ls -la
